      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $a,m,n\\ \\in \\N^{*}$, $a\\ge 2$, et $d = (a^n - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a,m,n\\ \\in \\N^{*}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a\\ge 2\\)</span>, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = (a^n - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4542b922-b8e8-4b54-83eb-a60ea423efc4",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $n = qm + r$ la division euclidienne de $n$ par $m$.\n      D{\\'e}montrer que $a^n \\equiv a^r (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {a^m - 1})$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n = qm + r\\)</span> la division euclidienne de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> par <span class=\"math inline\">\\(m\\)</span>. D<span>é</span>montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^n \\equiv a^r (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {a^m - 1})\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7bf19dc7-7fb5-41ca-aa56-65af4d5b80c2",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a^m - 1\\mid (a^{qm} - 1)a^r = a^n - a^r$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^m - 1\\mid (a^{qm} - 1)a^r = a^n - a^r\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3224810a-2082-40a7-8f12-8ed4235d3210",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire que $d = (a^r - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)$,\n      puis $d = a^{(n \\wedge m)} - 1$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = (a^r - 1) \\wedge (a^m - 1)\\)</span>, puis <span class=\"math inline\">\\(d = a^{(n \\wedge m)} - 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
